Timeframe: 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
Applicants should be aware that the time interval between the deadline for submission of applications and the award
of a grant may be several weeks in duration. This length of time is required to review and process grant applications.
